  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of the Investigational Drug Pagoclone, in the Treatment of Persistent Developmental Stuttering (PDS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>An 8-week, Double-Blind, Randomized, Multicenter, Flexible-Dose, Placebo-Controlled Pilot Study of Pagoclone in Patients With Persistent Developmental Stuttering Followed by a 52-week Open-Label Extension.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
